{"tid":2118221,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"政府澄清「禁足令」謠言","createTime":"2020-07-21T10:33:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T03:18:04.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":252,"uniUserReply":94,"replies":[{"pid":"f70fc6260b3402207c8f316af921e3f4636fb862","tid":2118221,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T10:33:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202007/21/P2020072100609.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202007%2F21%2FP2020072100609.htm&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23RjwoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=eaade35b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202007/21/P2020072100609.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n政府澄清「禁足令」謠言<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  對於有謠言指因應2019冠狀病毒病疫情，政府可能在未來數天實施所謂「禁足令」，政府發言人今日（七月二十一日）澄清絕無其事。<br />\n<br />\n  發言人說：「疫情嚴峻，我們應該齊心抗疫。市民千萬不要被虛假消息誤導，更不應發放或散播謠言，引起不必要的恐慌。」<br />\n<br />\n  發言人呼籲市民應繼續遵守社交距離的指引，減少外出，同時保持個人和環境衞生。市民亦應留意政府公布有關2019冠狀病毒病的最新消息。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2020年7月21日（星期二）<br />\n香港時間18時08分"},{"pid":"04ef6a151ceb9a194f1f637403d65fc9faacfd65","tid":2118221,"uid":273703,"like":345,"dislike":5,"score":340,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T10:33:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"51c70a076f1a1d617d9b00857885673c8edf6324","tid":2118221,"uid":307203,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T10:34:08.000Z","msg":"[劭勸行動 Day 2] 李永財區議員表態參選地產界，未有手足參選嘅功能組别尚餘11個<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2118209\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2118209</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"12bf25c20c615bb8a4d0baedfa2611881421da70","tid":2118221,"uid":273703,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T10:34:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0e8eefcfbf378ef3cd37e6746838ece880dcac8f","tid":2118221,"uid":307203,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"04ef6a151ceb9a194f1f637403d65fc9faacfd65","tid":2118221,"uid":273703,"like":345,"dislike":5,"score":340,"citedBy":3