.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"510a3bb9bdccbb9e5a8526a9b3726744cb441871","tid":2118221,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f70fc6260b3402207c8f316af921e3f4636fb862","tid":2118221,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T10:33:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202007/21/P2020072100609.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202007%2F21%2FP2020072100609.htm&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23RjwoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=eaade35b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202007/21/P2020072100609.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n政府澄清「禁足令」謠言<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  對於有謠言指因應2019冠狀病毒病疫情，政府可能在未來數天實施所謂「禁足令」，政府發言人今日（七月二十一日）澄清絕無其事。<br />\n<br />\n  發言人說：「疫情嚴峻，我們應該齊心抗疫。市民千萬不要被虛假消息誤導，更不應發放或散播謠言，引起不必要的恐慌。」<br />\n<br />\n  發言人呼籲市民應繼續遵守社交距離的指引，減少外出，同時保持個人和環境衞生。市民亦應留意政府公布有關2019冠狀病毒病的最新消息。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2020年7月21日（星期二）<br />\n香港時間18時08分"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T12:54:55.000Z","msg":"777自己都講過嫁？ <br />\n唔係咩"},{"pid":"1b9584bf9d0bad5a5aa89410ae30777488133396","tid":2118221,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"510a3bb9bdccbb9e5a8526a9b3726744cb441871","tid":2118221,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f70fc6260b3402207c8f316af921e3f4636fb862","tid":2118221,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T10:33:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202007/21/P2020072100609.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202007%2F21%2FP2020072100609.htm&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23RjwoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=eaade35b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202007/21/P2020072100609.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n政府澄清「禁足令」謠言<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  對於有謠言指因應2019冠狀病毒病疫情，政府可能在未來數天實施所謂「禁足令」，政府發言人今日（七月二十一日）澄清絕無其事。<br />\n<br />\n  發言人說：「疫情嚴峻，我們應